data.description: This is the perfect place to call home! And the seller's loan is assumable! 2.75% how low is that! Cute 3 bed, 1 bath home that was fully renovated just about 3 years ago. The bedrooms are very spacious and offer a lot of comfort. The bathroom is beautifully designed along with new fixtures! Roof is right under 5 years old. The hvac is currently not in use, however the seller is willing to repair/replace before closing. Come take a tour today and make this your own!
